See how the -DUSE_OPENCL carries through? (It doesn't do anything for my
package, but your get the idea.)  R even strips quotes, so you can also say

   $ PKG_CXXFLAGS="-DUSE_OPENCL" R CMD INSTALL

instead of 

   $ PKG_CXXFLAGS=-DUSE_OPENCL R CMD INSTALL

You can glance at the file $(R_HOME)/etc/Makeconf to see the other PKG_* variables.

